pes_of_Computer_skills_a_Mechanical_Engineer_should_have\" title=\"Types of Computer skills a Mechanical Engineer should have\">Types of Computer skills a Mechanical Engineer should have<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Being an Engineer demands certain standards academically, and as well as looking up to become one, you will need the steps by steps measures, and processes this article will enlighten you more on how to achieve your dream of becoming an Engineer.<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/header_3dd2e58f-ea83-452d-a280-2ead2ec2bae0.webp\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-2062 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/header_3dd2e58f-ea83-452d-a280-2ead2ec2bae0-300x253.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"253\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82170406\">Academic Requirements<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82170407\">Top Engineering jobs in Canada<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82170408\">Estimated Salary for Engineers<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82170409\">The Best Global Universities for Engineering in Canada<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82170410\">The basic subjects required for Mech. Engr.<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82170411\">Types of Computer skills a Mechanical Engineer should have<\/a><\/p>\n<p>The Canadian employee offer remunerative benefit packages which can exceed CAD $106,000<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"academic-requirements-how-to-become-a-mechanical-engineer\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Academic_Requirements_How_to_Become_a_Mechanical_Engineer\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82170406\"><\/a>Academic Requirements| How to Become a Mechanical Engineer<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>You must acquire a bachelor\u2019s degree in mechanical engineering or in related Engr. Discipline.<\/li>\n<li>Have good English or French language skills<\/li>\n<li>Attest to being drug-free<\/li>\n<li>Have a minimum of 2+ years of relevant experience.<\/li>\n<li>You must have a clean police record all through the past 5 years (exclusive of speeding crimes)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong><em>For information about immigration for mechanical Engineers kindly visit <a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwj2s-Tkm_TyAhUx5uAKHawyC1wQFnoECBMQAw&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immigration.ca%2Fmechanical-engineers&amp;usg=AOvVaw3v_tzGiXU1U9Q7XdU0unOS\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"top-engineering-jobs-in-canada\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Top_Engineering_jobs_in_Canada\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82170407\"><\/a>Top Engineering jobs in Canada<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Electrical Engr.<\/li>\n<li>Environmental<\/li>\n<li>Biomedical<\/li>\n<li>Chemical<\/li>\n<li>Systems<\/li>\n<li>Nuclear<\/li>\n<li>Computer<\/li>\n<li>Aerospace<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"estimated-salary-how-to-become-a-mechanical-engineer\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Estimated_Salary_How_to_Become_a_Mechanical_Engineer\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82170408\"><\/a>Estimated Salary| How to Become a Mechanical Engineer<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>They have a median salary of $88,430<\/li>\n<li>Best paid 25 percent made $111,980<\/li>\n<li>Estimated Lowest- paid $70,280.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"the-best-global-universities-for-engineering-in-canada\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Best_Global_Universities_for_Engineering_in_Canada\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82170409\"><\/a>The Best Global Universities for Engineering in Canada<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>McGill University<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Subject score: 56.9<\/li>\n<li>Global score: 74.9<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>University of Waterloo<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Subject score: 53.1<\/li>\n<li>Global score: 62.0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>University of Toronto<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Subject score: 46.2<\/li>\n<li>Global score: 83.5<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"the-basic-subjects-required-for-mech-engr\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_basic_subjects_required_for_Mech_Engr\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82170410\"><\/a>The basic subjects required for Mech. Engr.<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Statics and dynamics<\/li>\n<li>Materials engineering, composites<\/li>\n<li>Strength of materials and solid mechanics<\/li>\n<li>Mathematics (in particular, calculus, differential equations, and linear algebra)<\/li>\n<li>Basic physical sciences (including physics and chemistry)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"types-of-computer-skills-a-mechanical-engineer-should-have\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Types_of_Computer_skills_a_Mechanical_Engineer_should_have\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82170411\"><\/a>Types of Computer skills a Mechanical Engineer should have<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Python<\/li>\n<li>Visual Basic for Applications (VBA)<\/li>\n<li>Microsoft excel<\/li>\n<li>Finite Element Analysis software<\/li>\n<li>Computer-Aided Design (CAD) software<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #003300;\"><em><strong>See also &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; <\/strong><\/em><\/span><a title=\"How to safely preserve Food\" href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-safely-preserve-food\/\" rel=\"bookmark nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #003300;\"><strong>How to safely preserve Food<\/strong><\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"How to Become Mechanical Engineer in Canada &#8211; Academic Requirements, Estimated Salary, basic skills Computer skills, Top Engineering&hellip;\n"